---
title: Autumnal Italian Sausage with Israeli Couscous, Mushrooms and Wilted Spinach
description: On cool autumn nights, comfy food and easy clean up are all we can hope for. This warming one-pot meal easily does the trick! Quick and very delicious, we know you'll love this sausage dish as much as we do!
